'''''NiL''''' (定义为''NiL Isn't Liero'')是'''Liero'''克隆，运行在[[Linux|Linux]]下，初始没有[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows]]版本，使用[[GNU_General_Public_License|GNU General Public License]]协议。NiL支持[[Transmission_Control_Protocol|TCP]]网络，和无限制数目的玩家。曾掀起一阵热潮<ref name="cnn">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2000/TECH/computing/04/12/linux.net.games.idg/index.html|title=Open-source, networkable shooter has Linux gamers buzzing|author=Lee Anderson|date=April 12, 2000|work=CNN|accessdate=2009-04-01|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222053224/http://www.cnn.com/2000/TECH/computing/04/12/linux.net.games.idg/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> Flemming Frandsen在1999年启动此项目。<ref name="cnn"/>

